@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>We use personal data only as described here. We ask for your <strong>opt-in consent</strong> before using it; you can withdraw or ask about your data via the Contact page.</p>

<h2>What we collect and why</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Contact form</strong> (name, email, phone, subject, message): to answer your request. Sent via Web3Forms; not sold. Kept only as long as needed.</li>
    <li><strong>Account</strong> (login, profile): to run the service (e.g. high scores). Stored on our servers; not shared for marketing.</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies / local storage</strong>: we store only your consent choice (Accept/Decline); no personal data in it.</li>
</ul>

